{"id":144105,"type":3,"name":"Glimmer","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/38/06/144105_fktDc.jpg","rating":{"total":9,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":1,"6":2,"7":3,"8":1,"9":1,"10":0},"score":6.6},"summary":"喜欢日系动画主题歌却苦于国内一直没有同类作品的音乐迷们有福了，海岸线工作室出品的国产动画『纳米核心』以其出类拔萃的素质吸引了大批粉丝。其主题歌、BGM也制作极为精良倍受好评。\r\n\r\n目前粉丝们终于盼来了主题歌单曲的发布，除了已在片中使用粉丝们颇为熟悉的由日本著名DJ Kors K创作的OP Glimmer外，单曲还包含了仍未正式在片中出现的片尾ED曲 EXIST，据悉该曲由当前国内最炙手可热的音乐工作室Vanguard Sound领军人物G.K、Haloweak共同创作。更难得的是两首主题歌除了由本土的祈Inory、米雅演唱中文版外还有日本著名歌手森永真由美演唱日文版。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>纳米核心 原声带</li><li><span>艺术家: </span><a href=\"/person/25243\">祈Inory</a> / 米雅 / <a href=\"/person/6364\">森永真由美</a></li><li><span>作曲: </span>kors k / G.K、<a href=\"/person/6762\">斎藤広祐</a></li><li><span>厂牌: </span><a href=\"/person/11210\">Vanguard Sound</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>NANOCORE Original Soundtrack</li><li><span>版本特性: </span>Digital</li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2015-07-16</li><li><span>发行商: </span>Vanguard Sound</li><li><span>碟片数量: </span>1</li><li><span>作词: </span>沈病娇 / 零兮</li>","collection":{"collect":12,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"OP","count":2},{"name":"2015","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":0,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/0","type":0,"sort":0,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":""}],"disc":[{"title":"Disc 1","disc":[{"title":"1 Glimmer","href":"/ep/559811"},{"title":"2 EXIST","href":"/ep/559812"},{"title":"3 Glimmer - Japanese Ver.","href":"/ep/559813"},{"title":"4 EXIST - Japanese Ver.","href":"/ep/559814"},{"title":"5 Glimmer - Instrument Ver.","href":"/ep/559815"},{"title":"6 EXIST - Instrument Ver.","href":"/ep/559816"}]}],"staff":[{"id":6364,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/35/dd/6364_prsn_WzOi9.jpg","name":"森永真由美","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":25243,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/86/4d/25243_prsn_AH5OV.jpg","name":"梁蔓青","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":6762,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d0/2c/6762_prsn_TA90Z.jpg","name":"斋藤广佑","desc":"作曲"},{"id":11210,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f3/b1/11210_prsn_v8Zi2.j